item.description:
Sorry for the late posting of this month's meeting.  We've been displaced from our room at SNHU and have been trying to find an alternate location to host the meetings.  Penny will continue to work on finding an alternate location for our monthly meetings, but right now she is dealing with a family emergency.  I will be holding an informal brainstorming session (instead of our planned topic) for anyone interested in joining me at La Carreta on Thursday, February 17th at 6:00pm.

 

I will need to know if you are planning to join me so that I can give a head count when I get to the restaurant.  They will not seat us until the entire group is there.  Please RSVP as soon as possible.

 

Thanks,

Renae
